  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "莫辛-纳甘 7.62x54R 栓动式步枪（步兵型）",
      "en": "Mosin 7.62x54R bolt-action rifle (Infantry)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "莫辛步兵型",
      "en": "Mosin Infantry"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "莫辛-纳甘是知名度最广的俄罗斯步枪之一，是伟大的卫国战争期间苏联红军地面部队的主力装备。该款步枪研发于 1882 至 1891 年间，不仅先后装备俄罗斯帝国与苏联陆军，还广泛出口至多个国家。自 1891 年投入量产以来，莫辛-纳甘的总产量达 3700 万支，是战争史上产量最大的栓动式步枪之一。这款栓动式步枪老而弥坚，至今仍然活跃在全球各地的局部冲突战场上。",
      "en": "Mosin–Nagant is one of the most famous russian rifles, which was commonly used by Russian soldiers during WW2. Developed from 1882 to 1891, it was used by the armed forces of the Russian Empire, the Soviet Union and various other nations. It is one of the most mass-produced military bolt-action rifles in history with over 37 million units having been made since 1891. In spite of its age, it has been used in various conflicts around the world up to the present day."
    },
